# Arknights Operator Manager

> 🇧🇷 [Versão em Português abaixo](#gerenciador-de-operadores-arknights)

---

## Overview

A command-line Java application for managing an Arknights operator roster, built as an academic project to apply and test classic data structures and software engineering principles in a practical, domain-driven context.

## Goals

- Implement and apply classic data structures — **B-Tree**, **Patricia Trie**, and **KMP string search** — in a real use case rather than in isolation
- Model the Arknights operator system faithfully, including skills, masteries, modules, elite promotions, and deployment costs
- Follow **SOLID** principles throughout the design of the controller and utility layers
- Provide **persistent storage** via a tagged `.dat` format for full-fidelity save/load, and a human-readable `.md` roster export
- Build a foundation extensible toward a graphical user interface

## Features

### Data Structures
| Structure | Usage |
| :--- | :--- |
| `BTree<K, V>` | Primary operator registry — O(log n) insert, search, delete |
| `PatriciaTrie` | Name index — prefix-based lookup, autocomplete-ready |
| `KMP` | Substring search across skill names and descriptions |

### Operator Model
Each operator tracks:
- Name, rarity (1–6★), class and subclass
- Elite/promotion level (E0–E2) and level
- Deployment cost (DP) and potential (1–6)
- Up to 3 skills with individual levels (1–7, M1–M3) and a designated default
- Multiple modules with levels (1–3) and an equipped default

### Sorting
- **MergeSort** (generic, O(n log n)) with pluggable comparators
- Sort criteria: name, rarity, level, elite, DP cost, or compound (rarity + name, elite + level)

### Persistence
- **`.dat` export/import** — full-fidelity tagged format, human-readable and efficient to parse
- **`.md` roster export** — markdown table showing each operator's equipped skill and module
- Conflict resolution on import: skip or overwrite per operator

### Architecture
```
src/main/
├── main/           # Entry point and terminal interface (Main.java)
├── models/         # Operator, Skill, Module
├── structures/     # BTree, PatriciaTrie, KMP
├── controllers/    # OperatorDatabase, OperatorSerializer, RosterExporter
│                   # Interfaces: OperatorExporter, OperatorImporter
└── sorting/        # MergeSort, OperatorComparators
                    # Interface: Sorter
```

## Current Stage

| Layer | Status |
| :--- | :--- |
| Data structures | ✅ Implemented and tested (BTree: 36/36, Patricia Trie: tested) |
| Models | ✅ Complete |
| Controller layer | ✅ Complete, SOLID-compliant |
